OL,6,FA petition with more than 50,000
OL,7,Fsignatures calling for police officers
OL,8,Fand staff accused of violence against
OL,9,Fwomen and girls to be suspended while
OL,10,Fclaims are investigated has been
OL,11,Fdelivered to Downing Street by a
OL,12,Fwomen's charity.
OL,14,FRefuge took the document to
OL,15,FWestminster on Thursday, a year to the
OL,16,Fday since a damning review by Baroness
OL,17,FLouise Casey found that Britain's
OL,18,Flargest police force is
OL,19,Finstitutionally racist, homophobic and
OL,20,Fmisogynistic.
