OL,6,FThe charity, which supports victims of
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse, submitted the document
OL,8,Fas part of its Remove the Rot campaign.
OL,10,FUnder current procedures, there is no
OL,11,Fobligation for police forces to
OL,12,Fsuspend officers or staff being
OL,13,Finvestigated for allegations of
OL,14,Fviolence against women and girls.
