OL,3,CCall for suspension of all police and
OL,4,Cstaff accused of violence against women
OL,6,FAbigail Ampofo, interim chief
OL,7,Fexecutive of Refuge, said: "It is
OL,8,Fdeeply shocking to Refuge that it is
OL,9,Fnot currently mandatory for police
OL,10,Fofficers and staff to be suspended,
OL,11,Fpending investigation, when they are
OL,12,Faccused of violence against women and
OL,13,Fgirls.
OL,15,F"In any other profession, suspension
OL,16,Fwould be the norm, as would frequent
OL,17,Fvetting, so what makes policing any
OL,18,Fdifferent?
