OL,3,CCall for suspension of all police and
OL,4,Cstaff accused of violence against women
OL,6,F"As an institution who are supposed to
OL,7,Fprotect the public from harm, the
OL,8,Fpolice should be held to the highest
OL,9,Fof standards and any allegations of
OL,10,Fabuse against officers should be
OL,11,Ftreated with the utmost seriousness.
OL,13,F"At Refuge, it is our hope that this
OL,14,Fpetition, signed by so many people,
OL,15,Fwill show the Home Secretary that
OL,16,Fenough is enough.
OL,18,F"It is time that we remove the rot
OL,19,Ffrom police forces across the country
OL,20,Fand start restoring women's trust in
OL,21,Fpolicing to protect them."
