OL,6,FEarlier this month an inquiry by Lady
OL,7,FElish Angiolini found that a series of
OL,8,Fred flags were missed about serial sex
OL,9,Foffender Wayne Couzens before he went
OL,10,Fon to murder.
OL,12,FIn response the Home Office announced
OL,13,Fthat all officers charged with
OL,14,Findictable offences ` the most serious
OL,15,Fcrimes that can only be dealt with by
OL,16,Fcrown courts ` would be automatically
OL,17,Fsuspended from duty.
