OL,3,CCall for suspension of all police and
OL,4,Cstaff accused of violence against women
OL,6,FBut this would not include alleged
OL,7,Foffences such as indecent exposure,
OL,8,Fwith police chiefs having the power to
OL,9,Fdecide whether to suspend in those
OL,10,Fcases.
OL,12,FThe move does not extend to police
OL,13,Fstaff, and only applies once criminal
OL,14,Fcharges have been brought.
OL,16,FAccording to Refuge, around a quarter
OL,17,Fof police officers and staff facing
OL,18,Fsuch accusations were suspended from
OL,19,Fduty last year while the claims were
OL,20,Finvestigated.
